I"’<p>In the Hindu epic Mahabharata, Bheema, is the second of the Pandavas. The Mahabharata relates many events which portray the immense might of Bheema. Bhima is responsible for slaying all hundred Kaurava brothers in the Kurukshetra War.</p>

<p>At the time Bhima kills the rakshasa(evil) Hidimba, he meets his sister Hidimbi; they eventually get married and have a son, <a href="http://webjeda.com/gatok/about/">Ghatotkacha</a>.</p>

